RawQuestion: what language is spoken in greek?
ProcessedQuestion: what language is spoken in greek

Parses.Sparql:
PREFIX ns: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?x
WHERE {
FILTER (?x != ns:m.035qy)
FILTER (!isLiteral(?x) OR lang(?x) = '' OR langMatches(lang(?x), 'en'))
ns:m.035qy ns:location.country.languages_spoken ?x .
}
